				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I leveled a few hundred Xes commies under the new system. I have 12 Genius.
<br />

<br />
My results spanned from 9 to 22. 22 is the highest detection I saw. That's not to say it can't go higher, but 1 in 150 was 22.
<br />

<br />
A player with 15 Genius is more likely to get that high, but it won't be all that common. Commander abilities -do- still play into this. That 22 det was an Energy System Specialist/Psychic Progenitor.
<br />

<br />
I leveled a bunch of commanders with 7 Genius as well. 19 was the highest detection I saw.
<br />

<br />
Races with less Genius could still achieve fairly high levels of detection.<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://archspace.org/board/images/madkat/madkat.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
